column5: neighbor told me to paint whatever I wanted on his new shed before the siding goes up tomorrow...  I had Blaze Orange and Black........ It felt like a troublesome teen with a permission slip      Randy
Your an artist Randy.  You Been takin lessons from Bushart?
Are you going to paint your "tag" on the sturgeon trussell bridge?
Nice! Now go back and draw a net around that fish, so it feels more like home! HH
beautiful - belongs on a mailbox or bus stop somewhere...
Very nice work Randy! Did you ask him to get a neutral (or white) coloured siding so you can do the full colour version on a nicer background LOL
